    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-07-07T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-07-07T10:00:00-05:00" n="172"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d172">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20261/64: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wheeler</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stockholm</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-07-07T16:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 7, 1919, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 10:37 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3977. Your 1662 of July 1st was on July 5th communicated textually to the Soviet
                    Government through the Swedish Government wireless by Mr. <persName>Emanuele
                        Stang</persName> of Christiania, attorney for Lomonossoff.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Wheeler</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
